:label "B. NON-SPECIFIC ULCERS\n(commonest group)\n\n• Traumatic\n• Pyogenic / infective\n\n• Vascular origin:\n   ─ Venous (gravitational)\n   ─ Arterial (ischaemic)\n   ─ Decubitus\n   ─ Pressure sores\n\n• Neurotropic (trophic):\n   ─ Leprosy\n   ─ Diabetic neuropathy\n   ─ Cord lesions\n   ─ Peripheral neuropathies\n   ─ Syringomyelia\n\n• Metabolic / systemic disease:\n   ─ Diabetic ulcers\n   ─ Haemoglobinopathic (sickle)\n   ─ Hereditary spherocytosis\n   ─ Ulcerative colitis"
